g.text: • Please put the tools back after use
(its not fair on everyone else if they can't use or ﬁnd the tools, especially if they've been left in the main area or end up on the ﬂoor)
• Please do not disturb members while they use tools.
(If you think they are doing something wrong tell them once then walk away
yabbering at someone while they use the lathe for example could be dangerous)
• Do not Loan out tools without permission
• If you make a mess and leave tools in places where they can't be found.
(such as removing the air compressor nozzle and not replacing it, or taking the screwdrivers, not cleaning the ultrasonic cleaner etc)
This will make members very unhappy
